You see a room displaced from it's former surroundings. The walls are
covered with wood panelling, and brass trumpet lamps protruding from the
wall every few feet give the room light. Two walls are covered from floor
to ceiling with bookshelves, filled with books. The floor is covered by an
enormous rug covered with magnificent dragons and other scenes of
mysticism. An antique partners desk sits in the far corner, with a giant
leather swivel chair sits behind it. In the adjacent corner, rests a giant
black leather sofa. In front of the partners desk sits two smaller chairs
with high backs and arm rests.
