CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This sub-andorian structure is dark, cold and damp just as you would
expect it to be. The passing of numerous centuries has deformed it's once
straight and defined agains that formed the outer walls of this room.
Such deterioration gives one a distorted view of the space laid out
before you. A somewhat rundown looking machine of mechanical nature
rests nearby to a rather daunting, but pristine looking gate. Glancing
towards the other end your eye is caught by the glint of metal protruding
from the floor.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB DIG -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can't dig through solid concrete!
ENDIF


IFPREVERB PULL 3
  IFVAR ORG = 7
    IFNOITEM 9
      IFVAR PVAL52 > 0
        CLEARVERB
        EQUAL SUBWAYCOINS PVAL52
        EQUAL PVAL52 0
        MULT SUBWAYCOINS 10
        STRCVT 0 SUBWAYCOINS
        GMMSG **  Token machine is giving %0 gold coins to %n.
        ECHO PLAYER The panel seems to be stuck, but then suddenly gives way and flies open!
        ECHO OTHERS %n pulls on the panel, and finally manages to free it!
        NEWITEM 9 161 ADJ3=147
        SETITEMVAL 9 1 SUBWAYCOINS
        ECHO ALL %cGold coins spill out onto the floor.
        PLREVENT 1
        CONTPLREVENT
        ECHO ALL The panel slams back into place.
      ELSE
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER The panel seems to be stuck, but then suddenly gives way and flies open!
        ECHO OTHERS %n pulls on the panel, and finally manages to free it!
        PLREVENT 1
        CONTPLREVENT
        ECHO ALL The panel slams back into place.
      ENDIF
    ELSE
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER There is too much stuff on the floor for you to get to the panel.
    ENDIF
  ELSE
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER Not being very technically oriented, you are not sure what to pull on.
  ENDIF
ENDIF

