IFVERB RECALL -1
  IFVAR ARCHNUM ! 853
    IFVAR ARCHNUM ! 68
      IFVAR INTNUM68  > 4
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER %cYou recall much about the transportation systems of the pre-cataclysm
