  ECHO PLAYER Engraved on the sign in large blue letters, "TICKET OFFICE   |
  ECHO PLAYER                                                              |
  ECHO PLAYER                                                              V "
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LOOK 3
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You see an oddly shaped window that rests at eye level in
  ECHO PLAYER the western wall. The window is semi-circular, and has a
  ECHO PLAYER three inch gap between it and the shelf. You don't see anyone
  ECHO PLAYER inside the tiny office behind the window. You notice a dark
  ECHO PLAYER staircase leading downwards from the tiny office.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 3
  IFVAR WEALTH > 999
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You approach the window, and slip some coins under it.
    ECHO OTHERS %n walks up to the window and slides some coins underneath it.
    SUB WEALTH 1000
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL You see a ghostly hand slide a token onto the shelf and withdraws.
    NEWPUT 5 1174
  ELSE
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You don't think you have enough.
    ECHO OTHERS %n counts %h money and finds that %s hasn't enough.
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFVERB RECALL -1
  ECHO PLAYER %cYou think approaching the window might prove fruitful.
ENDIF

