		ECHO PLAYER to the pipes. After examing several of the pipes closely, you can
		ECHO PLAYER tell that a non-standard material is being used to carry something
		ECHO PLAYER very hot through some of the pipes.
	ENDIF
ENDIF

IFTOUCH 3
