*DESCRIPTION_START
The approximate center to this cavernous room. Giant stone columns line
the walls and black and white marble tiles spread out in every direction.
To the south you see a large sign suspended from the ceiling. On the
eastern wall, a sign next to a large stairway that leads down, reads
"Ferry line". Across from the stairway is a small door.
