NUMBER 3783
NAME Main Terminal, control room
INDOOR_FLOOR
ASTRAL
DARKNESS
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This looks like it was once the control room for the Main Terminus Subway system.
However, the room is completely beyond use or repair. Large boulders are strewn
about the floor where they fell from the walls crushing equipment and furniture.
The violent shaking that seems responsible for removing the doors from their
hinges seems to also be responsible for the large hole in the floor leading down
into a dank, dark and hot tunnel below the control room.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 2 1341 ADJ1=173 VAL2=3776

IFPREVERB LOOK 2
